body.p: The table above summarizes all of the PDU’s used by both the RI_RCP (TYPE=0) and the DI_RCP (TYPE=1-56).

The transmission order of PDUs on the DI_RCP interface is dependent on the type of PDU. Hard PDUs are sent in the following order: 1, 33, 2, 34, 5, 6, 17, 18, 19, 20, 9, 10, 11, 12, 25 and 26. Soft PDUs are sent after hard PDUs and the order is not guaranteed. For OTN pN_EBC and pFEBC soft PDUs, they are sent 0-15 in a round robin fashion.
